{"tid":1175237,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖有字] backpacking 印度北部遊記2019","createTime":"2019-05-28T12:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T08:26:42.000Z","uid":131533,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e13baf37611950f3c3a904f6bedfc39d3ed0ec","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:00:11.000Z","msg":"宜家喺印度玩緊 <br />\n今日係第五日<br />\n見有啲時間就打個遊記分享下做過乜啦<br />\n可能太長氣 唔鐘意就圖片mode啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第0日<br />\n大約晚上九點幾到新德里機場<br />\n原本預計留係機場直到第二朝0630坐內陸機去Varanasi<br />\n但心諗：仲有十日九日捱喎，俾自己舒服啲啦<br />\n又見到地圖附近有holiday inn就諗住都係爽多晚就行去搵車<br />\n無耐有個肥印度佬行埋嚟問我去邊，其實之前我睇有case話會扮晒嘢車你去第二間旅館/旅行社屈你錢，都有啲擔心，但個印度佬喺google度搵咗間酒店show晒佢幾星幾錢，講好價咁我就上咗佢手下㗎車，點知真係中招，完全車咗去第二間酒店，個名完全唔同，明明係許志安就當杜德偉，屌佢老味，我即刻發爛渣唔落車，叫我司機車返我去holiday inn<br />\n但佢手下即刻打電話去holiday inn問有無房，仲俾個電話我聽，雖然電話條友話無，但係我仲信你？我堅決死都話去咗先，佢就話我crazy係度互屌一輪，我就扮晒嘢話你車我去啦，我俾三千蚊你，點知佢又信喎，就到果陣佢好開心咁問係咪真三千，我即刻扮傻仔，what ? 三百呀（即原本價），佢嬲撚到停車叫我walk，我walk你老味咩，我唔理佢叫佢車到我去門口我先會行，撚狗成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知去到真係無房<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁大間酒店都可以無<br />\n好在隔離有一連幾間俾人轉機嘅酒店選擇，就係𠵱件事無啦啦搞到我夜瞓咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦到令我警戒心上到顛峰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第0日係hello moto<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c120dcbff61fc208825ade8ce4e4be302dabc6","tid":1175237,"uid":205996,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00No6Le.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00No6Le.gif&h=4ffd36a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5aaa9d142a3ab1d5572e5068285f7ebac494d31c","tid":1175237,"uid":190238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:11:51.000Z","msg":"有機場酒店呀，當時我都係係新德里落，第二朝去瓦拉納西，又唔想訓機場，就直接book機場酒店。<br />\n<br />\n一出黎直接搵職員帶我地上酒店就得，跟本唔駛出機場，第二朝直接落禁區轉機。<br />\n<br />\n咁安全得多又唔駛死咁多腦細胞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adABHjN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadABHjN.png&h=aa6ea551&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qkubwc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkubwc9.png&h=24b5411b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/McFmTrv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcFmTrv.png&h=2dd211a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/to7HCTb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fto7HCTb.png&h=36a4a3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/degEE6x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdegEE6x.png&h=0f561a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3jSfET.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3jSfET.png&h=20472c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oS9ZE6A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoS9ZE6A.png&h=9534e25c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXfmTrB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXfmTrB.png&h=b1196f96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KShP2j0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKShP2j0.png&h=e484e6f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a75d6d291f7793faceb7efae088ee5f013e735c","tid":1175237,"uid":43968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:22:14.000Z","msg":"留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a1d7c905841c6a449395d89af8dd9c7eccc57f","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:23:54.000Z","msg":"第1日<br />\n<br />\nT2其實都幾混亂<br />\n預咗個半鐘到機鐘<br />\n差唔多十個counter做緊checkin<br />\n但條龍長到最少百一二人<br />\n無計照排，但佢無耐就嗌我班機上前check in先<br />\n經過琴晚嘅不快事件同今朝機場個混亂情況<br />\n拎到pass果下我感受到我嘅旅程真係開始啦<br />\n<br />\n飛機接駁車內<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p3TPhRZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp3TPhRZ.png&h=654ef04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Bt36L0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Bt36L0.png&h=10661a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3thHCSV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3thHCSV.png&h=6a1712b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐indigo airline大約就五百蚊，早啲買仲平啲（好似係）𠵱間廉航機上係有水飲㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個小時唔夠嘅機程<br />\n學日本著名車手須藤京一話齋：同一個人我係唔會輸俾佢 twice<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次出去我唔會再輸錢輸時間<br />\n即刻叫咗個uber去hostel<br />\n埋單約六十蚊港紙<br />\n但一落車發現條褲濕濕地，唔係給個印仔司機靚仔<br />\n係㗎車冷氣好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />環保撚嚟嘅<br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"e63295ec69d9197cd72469aed44ed3d4b03f1c63","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5aaa9d142a3ab1d5572e5068285f7ebac494d31c","tid":1175237,"uid":190238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:11:51.000Z","msg":"有機場酒店呀，當時我都係係新德里落，第二朝去瓦拉納西，又唔想訓機場，就直接book機場酒店。<br />\n<br />\n一出黎直接搵職員帶我地上酒店就得，跟本唔駛出機場，第二朝直接落禁區轉機。<br />\n<br />\n咁安全得多又唔駛死咁多腦細胞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adABHjN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadABHjN.png&h=aa6ea551&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qkubwc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkubwc9.png&h=24b5411b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/McFmTrv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcFmTrv.png&h=2dd211a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/to7HCTb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fto7HCTb.png&h=36a4a3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http