mbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcFmTrv.png&h=2dd211a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/to7HCTb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fto7HCTb.png&h=36a4a3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/degEE6x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdegEE6x.png&h=0f561a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3jSfET.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3jSfET.png&h=20472c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oS9ZE6A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoS9ZE6A.png&h=9534e25c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXfmTrB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXfmTrB.png&h=b1196f96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KShP2j0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKShP2j0.png&h=e484e6f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"我完全無見到有依樣嘢 <br />\n係咪因為我T3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得自己好撚柒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"我唔記得邊度出啦，不過就算係T3，都有Holiday inn express 呀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/in/eaton-smart-new-delhi-airport.en-gb.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.booking.com%2Fhotel%2Fin%2Featon-smart-new-delhi-airport.en-gb.html&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2F6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=8da33be6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.booking.com/hotel/in/eaton-smart-new-delhi-airport.en-gb.html</a><br />\n<br />\n但睇裝修，好似係我住果間，可能改左名。"},{"pid":"832589486a0f122f18a5fe1fb25410d74ba4c18e","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:18:13.000Z","msg":"第1日<br />\n<br />\n續<br />\n<br />\n到埗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kESMkfq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkESMkfq.png&h=7bd96009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6aRwoh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6aRwoh.png&h=b67ce5aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感覺𠵱度啲hostel都鐘意咁嘅配色<br />\n見唔少都係咁<br />\n<br />\n個staff其實幾好人嘅<br />\n但本來小六級英文程度嘅我<br />\n加埋佢啲印度口音<br />\n有一刻懷疑我其實廿六個字母都未學識<br />\n安頓好後join埋個黃昏恒河tour就自己出去行下啦<br />\n<br />\n第一餐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UherkiU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUherkiU.png&h=0dc5d5f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係間日本人開嘅餐廳<br />\n心諗應該無伏掛<br />\n食完，日本人果然係品質保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咖哩雞有咖哩雞味，食落喉嚨好c服<br />\n約三十蚊港紙<br />\n其實點解日本人咁熱愛印度<br />\n明明佢地差異咁大，有無巴打可以話我知呢？<br />\n<br />\n除咗恒河我對Varanasi一無所知<br />\n就跟旅遊去咗個叫「鹿野苑」嘅地方<br />\n去咗票務處已經俾印度人打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個staff又手腳慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOkok嚟旅行就係嚟感受自己生活以外嘅世界嘛<br />\n突然有一下覺得香港嘅好<br />\n<br />\n入去lu<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSOonAR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSOonAR.png&h=32db3ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實入面只係有啲紅磚遺跡嘅爛鳩地<br />\n同埋相後面果座爛塔<br />\n<br />\n去放水時廁所門口個大叔好鬼好禮貌<br />\n見到我竟然Namaste <br />\n係咪想R貼士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家警戒心好重呀<br />\n門口仲有飲用水機 不了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZhTKQg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZhTKQg.png&h=4fde3fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔離仲有間寺 免費就行埋啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EY5euia.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEY5euia.png&h=32cebaab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實都係無乜嘢睇 就咁call uber返去<br />\n等車嘅同時有班印度青年上前搭我訕<br />\n鳩吹幾句仲迫我互follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉事撚但啦<br />\n好快車嚟咗我地就道別了<br />\n咁樣來回用咗三十幾四十蚊<br />\n<br />\n第一次去多印度人嘅地方<br />\n已經感受到人地講嘅望到你唔舒服<br />\n佢地對外國人係好好奇 會講你唔知乜<br />\n由其後生仔 不過我諗都係無乜惡意嘅<br />\n而班印仔到宜家隔咗幾日都有問候下我<br />\n<br />\n返去都係十二點未夠<br />\n就攤係度玩手機等五點鐘join tour<br />\n咁唔充實嘅旅行真係無幾多次<br />\n好唔似自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"6faabeff1118c2fae3239202a14cdca96645cf37","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64ff37b2d2b3c73490ee88bcbf4e4230ed233ecb","tid":1175237,"uid":190238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e63295ec69d9197cd72469aed44ed3d4b03f1c63","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5aaa9d142a3ab1d5572e5068285f7ebac494d31c","tid":1175237,"uid":190238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:11:51.000Z","msg":"有機場酒店呀，當時我都係係新德里落，第二朝去瓦拉納西，又唔想訓機場，就直接book機場酒店。<br />\n<br />\n一出黎直接搵職員帶我地上酒店就得，跟本唔駛出機場，第二朝直接落禁區轉機。<br />\n<br />\n咁安全得多又唔駛死咁多腦細胞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/adABHjN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FadABHjN.png&h=aa6ea551&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qkubwc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkubwc9.png&h=24b5411b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/McFmTrv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcFmTrv.png&h=2dd211a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/to7HCTb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fto7HCTb.png&h=36a4a3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/degEE6x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdegEE6x.png&h=0f561a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3jSfET.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3jSfET.png&h=20472c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oS9ZE6A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoS9ZE6A.png&h=9534e25c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXfmTrB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXfmTrB.png&h=b1196f96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KShP2j0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKShP2j0.png&h=e484e6f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"我完全無見到有依樣嘢 <br />\n係咪因為我T3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得自己好撚柒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:17:09.000Z","msg":"我唔記得邊度出啦，不過就算係T3，都有Holiday inn express 呀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.booking.com/hotel/in/eaton-smart-new-delhi-airport.en-gb.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.booking.com%2Fhotel%2Fin%2Featon-smart-new-delhi-airport.en-gb.html&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2F6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=8da33be6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.booking.com/hotel/in/eaton-smart-new-delhi-airport.en-gb.html</a><br />\n<br />\n但睇裝修，好似係我住果間，可能改左名。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:20:20.000Z","msg":"有呀...我就係柒咗行咗出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n守門口啲警察就唔再俾我入去"},{"pid":"7baffd11f5561fa54a1236850b8638f6d1006a18","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ce81f78686e517e66cbf579b9bfb3f197b081fd","tid":1175237,"uid":243516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:28:56.000Z","msg":"樓主係去Leh戈邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T19:02:21.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又無咁北...."},{"pid":"2a102591eaa6218d5c7f996ee62e0e9782659049","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:06:00.000Z","msg":"第1日<br />\n<br />\n續<br />\n<br />\n第一眼嘅恒河<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBb5A4A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBb5A4A.png&h=50fd32f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嚟到臭名遠播嘅恒河<br />\n究竟佢係印度人心目中係有幾神聖呢？<br />\n聞落無乜味，無想像中咁污糟<br />\n近睇綠綠地似維港水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aV1Uup0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaV1Uup0.png&h=73f5ef4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成船鬼仔<br />\n導遊啲英文口音又聽得明少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係專心我嘅遊船河<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYdonLF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYdonLF.png&h=905bb45c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n𠵱度啲狗都係瘦到包晒骨<br />\n好少對人吠，自己靜靜地搵垃圾食<br />\n仲見到有時俾人踢<br />\n下世投胎唔好做印度狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cbMEFyb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcbMEFyb.png&h=e289df3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成團去咗對面岸休息<br />\n咁有得騎下馬騎下駱駝咁嘅...<br />\n落船果陣要涉水過<br />\n咁就掂到啲聖水啦......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/31/103706_7711d55df752705866b4113d0f6cb4d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F31%2F103706_7711d55df752705866b4113d0f6cb4d5.png&h=1edc4104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快上返船去火場葬<br />\n導遊邊講解，我地就邊吸燒出嚟啲煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愈係高位置燒嘅人就愈有錢<br />\n包得愈靚嚟燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇埋河祭就返去hostel了<br />\n祭典後嘅街道同未取消行人專用區既菜街咁上下<br />\n另加勁多電單車/篤篤狂砵，人車共用一條路<br />\n揸車就似玩雷電咁<br />\n又無意外依下好嘢<br />\n無得唔服印度佬啲駕駛技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢地唔會好似香港揸車咁俾人篤/砵就屌晒老母玩鬥氣乜乜乜<br />\n應該都麻目晒<br />\n後尾太攰無點影相<br />\n未夠九點就早早返去瞓<br />\n準備聽朝又去恒河<br />\n第1日 完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6526ffc4c12e31a7eea1bbddd45b535ce1c34ae","tid":1175237,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"留名 樓豬宜家去左幾多日？"},{"pid":"67a24f09e0b92039b1686004e1c88f25dfa75be0","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6526ffc4c12e31a7eea1bbddd45b535ce1c34ae","tid":1175237,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"留名 樓豬宜家去左幾多日？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"會去十一日<br />\n今日第七"},{"pid":"9ce4d590da2d4dc3d7fb45367db1e0c314b736b1","tid":1175237,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67a24f09e0b92039b1686004e1c88f25dfa75be0","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6526ffc4c12e31a7eea1bbddd45b535ce1c34ae","tid":1175237,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"留名 樓豬宜家去左幾多日？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"會去十一日<br />\n今日第七"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"絲打？ 想問下一個去有冇危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe0090ce7aff11eee7fafbb9d3b9b994b907e53","tid":1175237,"uid":12052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"印度人真係唔屌唔得，無個信得過，去左9日，屌足9日，不過又幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，一個月前去完"},{"pid":"7cf046b23a9a62cf9f831a5e3f91f4c4c44c9ccd","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ce4d590da2d4dc3d7fb45367db1e0c314b736b1","tid":1175237,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67a24f09e0b92039b1686004e1c88f25dfa75be0","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6526ffc4c12e31a7eea1bbddd45b535ce1c34ae","tid":1175237,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"留名 樓豬宜家去左幾多日？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"會去十一日<br />\n今日第七"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"絲打？ 想問下一個去有冇危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>唔係</strong><br />\n遲啲會講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">極度唔建議一個女仔去</span>"},{"pid":"c99cdcd319029d883de641a502b2fe94aa59430a","tid":1175237,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cf046b23a9a62cf9f831a5e3f91f4c4c44c9ccd","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ce4d590da2d4dc3d7fb45367db1e0c314b736b1","tid":1175237,"uid":18691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67a24f09e0b92039b1686004e1c88f25dfa75be0","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"會去十一日<br />\n今日第七"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"絲打？ 想問下一個去有冇危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>唔係</strong><br />\n遲啲會講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">極度唔建議一個女仔去</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:44:09.000Z","msg":"好 淨返幾日注意安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bc0a34ea0e70016698bb951480f7cdc0b4065e","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fe0090ce7aff11eee7fafbb9d3b9b994b907e53","tid":1175237,"uid":12052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:28:59.000Z","msg":"印度人真係唔屌唔得，無個信得過，去左9日，屌足9日，不過又幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，一個月前去完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:44:28.000Z","msg":"又唔係<br />\n都有遇唔少好人"},{"pid":"5c2d02434bef93edf4e53c9b0965a8d7902a418a","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T05:36:41.000Z","msg":"第2日<br />\n<br />\n恒河日出<br />\n<br />\n四點半天濛光又起身跟hostel tour出去<br />\n<br />\n印度有個地方好，就係hostel好平<br />\n比你食一餐分分鐘嘅仲要平<br />\n(暫時住過最平$19港紙一晚)<br />\n但質素絕對可以接受，水準同台灣hostel差唔多<br />\n放行李 common area 沖涼完全無托手踭<br />\n可能競爭都大，成日有空床位嘅情況<br />\n仲日日有tour跟住出去玩添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就日出，有人游緊水<br />\n(定同時係水底做第二啲嘢?)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2yTmNr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2yTmNr.png&h=3d77b0f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZ1JJ1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZ1JJ1b.png&h=3d05a3b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次導遊身兼船夫<br />\n飲恒河水加日日划船<br />\n你睇下幾大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n健身奶粉，不用了<br />\n其實印度都好多型男想睇我貼多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/31/131701_2b3711d95ab9163ac1ccadb7c165bf11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F31%2F131701_2b3711d95ab9163ac1ccadb7c165bf11.png&h=0fdb72d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n導遊無琴日果個英文咁好<br />\n亦都係主力俾你自己去睇<br />\n有問題再問，我比較鐘意咁多啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/31/132252_2e795fb26d4e9c091790b96fddbc87ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F31%2F132252_2e795fb26d4e9c091790b96fddbc87ae.png&h=9743457f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天光了，早上的恒河有人在洗澡、刷牙、洗衫、拜神和學游水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jm4y6k3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjm4y6k3.png&h=1dcf8bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"012f77b734745b624e4b0c78a4245c2f4db96318","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:09:06.000Z","msg":"第2日 <br />\n<br />\n繼續<br />\n<br />\n完咗tour後<br />\n就去搵食，時間都未夠七點鐘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/31/134413_2a0ed4fa6f9e0f6ebb275931566302f4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F31%2F134413_2a0ed4fa6f9e0f6ebb275931566302f4.png&h=ad00e8cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺印度街上截車嘅經驗好差<br />\n一嚟俾水魚價你<br />\n二嚟上咗車再同你講一輪，我試過講唔掂即落車<br />\n三嚟佢地會唔識扮識<br />\n我諗我話去重慶大廈佢地會話無問題，上咗車先講<br />\n四係最壞情況，反口，扮傻，唔找錢，仲要聲大夾惡過我，嘈多兩嘈有人行埋嚟一齊嘰哩咕嚕<br />\n單拖嘅我只可以敗走，走住屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xyt8byg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXyt8byg.png&h=e7c907b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然係20rupee (即係2蚊多少少港紙) <br />\n但老實好緊要，一份工作幾低下都應該被尊重，大前題係你識尊重自己做嘅嘢，認真努力咁工作。<br />\n自從𠵱次後，我無再係街截車，如果要嚟印度我建議你<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>坐uber坐uber坐uber </strong></span>或者ola ，後者就要俾現金<br />\n明買明賣一句都唔洗講唔洗煩<br />\n亦有人講過係Varanasi同Jaipur𠵱啲遊客重鎮先係咁<br />\n不過俾人呃一次係你唔好彩<br />\n兩次就係人衰，三次就係你柒啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mvqa8Ds.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmvqa8Ds.png&h=fd25623a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嚟到一間旅遊書同trip advisor都多推嘅民宿<br />\n印度九成九guest house又好hotel又好<br />\n都係天台做餐廳下面幾層做住宿嘅形式<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTsg4kj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTsg4kj.png&h=3baf7cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老闆係友善嘅<br />\n但都好積極咁做生意，令我有啲吃不消<br />\n邊食邊傾計就例牌<br />\n佢仲會講下佢自己開店理念<br />\n民宿有乜活動搞，我幾時走，會唔會學下瑜珈先走<br />\n我會點揀𠵱度啲民宿呀<br />\n我本旅遊書上點寫佢<br />\n最後當然捉住我寫comment俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見佢咁積極，嘢食又算係咁，算啦<br />\n<br />\n俾完評分老細終於放過我<br />\n接落嚟下晝先去飛Jaipur<br />\n大嗱嗱五六個鐘，跟住書去打發時間<br />\n<br />\n去咗間寺，乜名唔記得<br />\n淨係知無錯，係伏嚟<br />\n大家記得嚟Varanasi去恒河就得<br />\n留大半日，睇個日出同日落都好夠好夠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14Hg4or.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14Hg4or.png&h=9a0d26d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gsisrDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgsisrDj.png&h=24df50d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然之後都係坐uber<br />\n但其中有司機，gps都唔識路<br />\n落車問我做乜唔俾錢，仲叫我俾五星佢<br />\n我nice guy嚟㗎嘛係咪？<br />\nOkok no problem, five star rate<br />\nYou good me good <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我show一show俾佢睇果五粒星<br />\n佢安心咁上返佢㗎車<br />\n<br />\n行過兩個街口後 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSyTnDy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSyTnDy.png&h=d4cd11f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我急不及待咁拎返手機出嚟<br />\n啱啱我都未㩒confirm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我從來都唔俾comment<br />\n今次我盡用我識嘅英文去評價<br />\n係佢安心以為拎到五星回程嘅同時<br />\n俾一粒星係我對uber𠵱個apps嘅愛同責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nVaranasi機場等上機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypE7r9F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypE7r9F.png&h=e0a3fa7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機場嚟講印度算幾深嚴<br />\n首先有機票同証件先會俾入<br />\n各航空公司會各自check scan咗寄倉行李先俾check  in<br />\n過保安果陣scan得幾認真<br />\nJaipur 我來啦<br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"828fd79bb307fa3215a5d717ffe8ab71a75bc1de","tid":1175237,"uid":119933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"4c24a7f6ad0487692f9afd9b065b9cbb61be8675","tid":1175237,"uid":80735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"留明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇多d圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042b3a38d163b433f6f8233f6f1a7846c78ea9c5","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T10:31:51.000Z","msg":"第2日 <br />\n<br />\n繼續<br />\n<br />\n又係indigo airline<br />\n落地後去hostel放低啲行李先<br />\n架車行咗十五分鐘<br />\n對jaipur 第一印象唔係：嘩pink city<br />\n而係返返先進世界<br />\n畢直嘅馬路，紅綠燈等等<br />\n雖然仍然會揸到舞龍咁左穿右插<br />\n但交通同市容都比Varanasi好太多<br />\n而且仲起緊地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放好行李就係common area hea咗一陣<br />\n傍晚Join個food tour 解決今晚嘅晚餐<br />\n跟當地人搵食，應該唔伏掛<br />\n另外仲有一對英國情侶一齊共四個人去<br />\n我毒又唔係好敢同人講英文搞到氣氛有啲怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每人夾咗約四十蚊港紙出嚟搭車加食嘢<br />\n大約食咗八樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相真係影唔到多，因為好多都要搵手食<br />\n唔想整到部機痴立立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFood market嚟嘅，要俾10Rupee入場費<br />\n都幾乾淨同多人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spHUfWf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspHUfWf.png&h=e7111700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲Chai<br />\n四十幾度仲飲熱辣辣嘅茶，邊條咖哩腸諗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過又真係幾好飲嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DsfZr25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDsfZr25.png&h=152078c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見有鋁袋裝幾新奇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYPO4P2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeYPO4P2.png&h=032be00a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食雪糕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7DhH9gU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7DhH9gU.png&h=68fbf3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有乜特別，但三個人食一杯<br />\n好快鬼仔同鬼妹就唔食<br />\n我諗佢地覺得同我口水交流好核突<br />\n其實我又何嘗唔係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地停咗手，唔通我話唔要唔食啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就一幅津津有味嘅樣子食埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多嘢食都唔記得叫乜名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cP529g7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcP529g7.png&h=0e758d77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKE7AXc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKE7AXc.png&h=d47001f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依對情侶真係幾gentle，好有耐性咁聽我鳩噏，再加埋啲英國口音聽得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成個tour都幾開心，大英祖國萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第2日<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"65a66ca0bccfbfb444ad579d76cdd9fd1c3f0113","tid":1175237,"uid":131533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"第3日<br />\n<br />\nJaipur算係多數遊客留得最耐嘅城市<br />\n我都會留兩日係度<br />\n宜家12-4點係不適宜戶外活動<br />\n所以最好就早啲起身去景點<br />\n<br />\n水井<br />\n長期有人駐守，無得落去影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/soysBeb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsoysBeb.png&h=57f81e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就有個細路嚟搭訕<br />\n依度啲細路完全唔怕人，同好有好奇心<br />\n不停問你嘢，仲話帶我行條捷徑上amber palace<br />\n最後當然係問你拎錢啦<br />\n見佢咁醒目都俾咗少少錢佢<br />\n<br />\nAmber palace <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ih9GFLZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fih9GFLZ.png&h=474fad9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有得行上去左上角果度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrMYHZC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrMYHZC.png&h=678b7802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rV9WuFb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrV9WuFb.png&h=7d6e7427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好仔細嘅圖案<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D6dXd7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD6dXd7e.png&h=34d43a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37DPPMN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37DPPMN.png&h=649bd5b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kr8TwUz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkr8TwUz.png&h=faec3811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係起喺山上，係可以喺入口坐象入城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TsJL7to.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTsJL7to.png&h=3917853c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再行上去望返落嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imeSNy5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimeSNy5.png&h=0384c936&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市區方向<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkNpDGj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkNpDGj.png&h=d40acff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n𠵱度啲實Q好興跟住你行 指下啲嘢係乜係乜<br />\n搏你俾錢佢，扮聽唔明就得<br />\n你有你行佢有佢行，得閒嚟個施丹轉身<br />\n唔好俾佢lead住就收到佢皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n差唔多十二點一點就落返去食飯就返hostel抖抖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iceLn9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiceLn9C.png&h=3f9c6d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃昏再成班人出去水之宮殿<br />\n麻麻地靚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3gj7BzB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3gj7BzB.png&h=db5a801f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n俾印度仔邀請幫佢影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34yDJe8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34yDJe8.png&h=2e629052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又幾鬼馬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xSv6R8z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxSv6R8z.png&h=5b6556a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度仔好鐘意你影佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z73PQsD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ73PQsD.png&h=8e33a116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一齊坐tuktuk期間有個法國仔問我雨傘革命嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快就返咗去lu<br />\n風之宮 係正市中心 <br />\n順帶一提想影正面未必要去對面cafe幫襯（貴夾難食）<br />\n有個位可以唔入門口都影到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVSkW8K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVSkW8K.png&h=0bf40dee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第3日 <br />\n<br />\n完"}]}